he.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515c4f4a428278287356b5dc421c3c17beab4976","tid":1048441,"uid":107157,"like":157,"dislike":9,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"重力波關係<br />\nF=PA<br />\n當F&gt;0 而 P&lt;0 果時,<br />\n空間就會因為壓力而扭曲，<br />\n形成一個反物質壓力狀態，<br />\n根據白努利定理，<br />\nP1+pv1^2+0.5pgh1=P2+pv2^2+0.5pgh2<br />\n假設兩條雙黃線係位於同一水平面而進行扭曲，<br />\nh=0<br />\n而當P1呈反物質壓力狀態，而同時另一條雙黃線並無受壓，而雙黃線皆為同樣密度物料既情況下<br />\nP1&lt;0 , P2=0<br />\n最終得出以下結論:<br />\nP1=-v1^2+v2^2<br />\nv1&gt;v2<br />\n根據能量守恆定律:<br />\n0.5m1v1^2=0.5m2v2^2<br />\n0.5m1v1^2&lt;0.5m2v1^2<br />\nm1&lt;m2<br />\n由於m1同m2應為同樣物質，<br />\n所以應該有勢能存在，<br />\n結論:<br />\n有股神秘力量搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c314a77e312949ecc25e0d356062ba715807ef35","tid":1048441,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"瀝青啲色一舊舊 關唔關事？"},{"pid":"c6ff1d2e2545eee67abe980e54af75f933a1ff60","tid":1048441,"uid":33808,"like":157,"dislike":31,"score":126,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"點解樓主咁多負皮？<br />\n頭幾個回覆仲奇怪<br />\n明明就係啲黃線畫到錯晒<br />\n我真係睇唔到點樣咩重型車壓得多"},{"pid":"1676de8622a2057a0bf446896341a955caf52b2e","tid":1048441,"uid":33808,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"31d2b382d199fc39c9b9232e06fd32b39c686d40","tid":1048441,"uid":40697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/234702_d9dd599e211ae378ab8205bfb5b5903e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F234702_d9dd599e211ae378ab8205bfb5b5903e.png&h=8538307a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"點解咁多無哩頭回覆同負評"},{"pid":"ecbe5982502a211c7a98404243179dfec3d70110","tid":1048441,"uid":134474,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:43:56.000Z","msg":"點撚樣轆到變型？點睇都係畫錯"},{"pid":"907b2b5a